sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Browser UI
  participant API as NestJS (ChatController)
  participant DB as Postgres (chat_messages)
  participant LLM as OpenAI-compatible API

  UI->>API: GET /api/articles/:id/chat/stream?message=...&requestId=...
  API->>DB: upsert USER message (articleId, requestId)
  API->>LLM: stream completion (context = original + fake + last N messages)
  loop SSE deltas
    LLM-->>API: delta chunk
    API-->>UI: SSE {type:"delta", delta:"..."}
  end
  API->>DB: upsert ASSISTANT message (articleId, requestId)
  API-->>UI: SSE {type:"done", messageId:"..."}

